    <intervention_name>Stereotactic Body Radiation Therapy</intervention_name>
    <description>The schedule will be 3 fractions of 15 Gy up to a total dose of 45 Gy delivered every day with VMAT and Flattening filter-free (FFF) beams. Image-guided systems, including CBCT, will be used for all patients.</description>
